=== 影响 ===
《Air/真心為你》影响了魏斯·安德森的电影《[[犬之島|犬之島]]》的创作<ref>{{cite web |title=10 films that influenced Wes Anderson's Isle Of Dogs |url=https://www.dazeddigital.com/film-tv/article/39514/1/10-films-that-influenced-wes-anderson-and-isle-of-dogs |website=Dazed |language=en |date=2018-03-30 |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611153418/https://www.dazeddigital.com/film-tv/article/39514/1/10-films-that-influenced-wes-anderson-and-isle-of-dogs |archive-date=2019-06-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。EVA贰号机战斗场面名留日本动画史<ref>{{cite web |script-title=ja:【不朽の名作】熱狂ファンであればあるほど裏切られた感の強かった「新世紀エヴァンゲリオン劇場版 Air/まごころを、君に」 |url=https://npn.co.jp/article/detail/69049614/ |website=リアルライブ |date=2015-09-11 |language=ja |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912195030/http://npn.co.jp/article/detail/69049614/ |archive-date=2015-09-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，影响了后世一些动画师，如[[龜田祥倫|龜田祥倫]]<ref>{{cite web |script-title=ja:亀田祥倫（１）『エヴァ』と今石洋之がきっかけだった |url=http://animestyle.jp/2014/12/08/8346/ |website=WEBアニメスタイル |language=ja |date=2014-12-08 |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302052448/http://animestyle.jp/2014/12/08/8346/ |archive-date=2018-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、横田拓己<ref>{{cite web |script-title=ja:アニメーター・横田拓己 ロングインタビュー！（アニメ・ゲームの“中の人” 第38回） |url=https://akiba-souken.com/article/43116/ |website=アキバ総研 |date=2019-12-22 |language=ja |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206162953/https://akiba-souken.com/article/43116/ |archive-date=2020-02-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
该作也被一些作品引用和致敬，如美国动画《[[史帝芬宇宙|史帝芬宇宙]]》<ref>{{cite web |author=Lynzee Loveridge |title=7 Anime References in American Cartoons |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/the-list/2017-02-04/.111753 |website=Anime News Network |date=2017-02-04 |language=en |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611014100/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/the-list/2017-02-04/.111753 |archive-date=2019-06-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、电影《[[不速之客_(2002年電影)|不速之客]]》<ref>{{cite web |title=Comedian/Actor Robin Williams Passes Away at 63 |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-08-12/comedian-actor-robin-williams-passes-away-at-63/.77541 |website=Anime News Network |date=2014-08-12 |language=en |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608004158/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-08-12/comedian-actor-robin-williams-passes-away-at-63/.77541 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。中國动画电影《[[十萬個冷笑話_(電影)|十万个冷笑话]]》也进行了致敬，其片尾曲《来吧，甜蜜的吐槽》即改编自本作的插曲《来吧，甜蜜的死亡》<ref>{{cite web |author=Xiong Yuqing |title=Ode to animation |url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/901192.shtml |website=Global Times |date=2015-01-11 |language=en |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191106074643/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/901192.shtml |archive-date=2019-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=《十冷》中的名人名片 影迷导演致敬经典 |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2015-01-08/doc-iavxeafr9751446.shtml |work=新浪娱乐 |date=2015-01-08 |access-date=2020-01-19 |archive-date=2021-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211217023751/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2015-01-08/doc-iavxeafr9751446.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。受影响的还有[[彩虹乐团|彩虹乐团]]的歌曲《{{lang|ja|あなた}}》，负责作曲的[[tetsu|tetsu]]看过电影后，抱着希望明日香打开心扉的想法创作了该曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://anibu.jp/eva-character-song-17986.html|script-title=ja:実はけっこうある!?「エヴァ」キャラへ向けた歌！|date=2015-06-17|language=ja|access-date=2020-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802171543/http://anibu.jp/eva-character-song-17986.html|archive-date=2017-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

